## Using This Project

The simplest way to comply with this license is to:

1. Keep the LICENSE file in your project
2. Mention in your README that you're using this software
3. If you modify it, consider noting what changes you made

Example attribution:
```
This project is built with YourBrand E-Commerce Platform
(https://github.com/your-repo)
Licensed under the MIT License
```

